Attachments
precis:
Authority (a) to accept the transfer from the Province of British
Columbia of the administration and control over some 26.81 hectares of
land situate in the Cassiar District (Lot 3332); and (b) to set those
lands apart for the use and benefit of the Iskut Band of Indians as an
addition to Iskut Indian Reserve No. 6 in British Columbia.
